    {
      "id": "68",
      "name": "考据",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "应达",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/31/157749474/b12de6755cb161419914c25311904f6c_4303656288281964328.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "夜叉是璃月的仙人，自古以来与岩王帝君和其他仙人一起守护着这片土地。在魔神战争时期，他们与摩拉克斯并肩作战，并在归终死后出现在场。是夜叉挡住了她身上的结界，阻止了黑暗能量的蔓延。在所有夜叉中，最强的有五个：浮舍、金鹏、弥怒、应达和伐难。他们被简称为「仙众夜叉」。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "right",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/31/157749474/8d634ac63619a568db0514ab5bc140fd_9159796654269277713.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "太古年间，璃月瘴疠丛生，遍布妖异。战败魔神朽烂的残躯将憎恨与怨怒散布尘世，化为妖邪。每当妖邪躁动不安，瘟疫、鬼怪与异变就会随之而生。于是，岩王帝君唤来仙人中的夜叉来除灭妖邪。他们向岩王立誓",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)",
                        "italic"
                      ],
                      "text": "「通过屠杀来恢复秩序，通过战斗来净化邪恶。为此，我们会献出生命。」",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "作为所有仙人中最凶猛和好战的仙人，他们准备不择手段来保护这片土地。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "多年来，夜叉们忠实地守护着岩王帝君，平息了世间种种灾难。但有一天，尽管他们很强大，但他们发现自己的行为已经造成了伤害，魔神的遗恨污染了他们。由于受到战败神的仇恨的影响，他们被业障所拘束。业障对夜叉来说是一种毒药，是他们杀人无数的惩罚；它带给他们剧烈的痛苦，感染他们的意识，并引起愤怒、痛苦和恐惧。有些人陷入了一种无法用言语表达的愤怒而盲目，或陷入恐惧而发狂。有些人因自相残杀而死。有些人走火入魔。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/31/157749474/aa00000ed3f5c0ef846323ee4b5c110e_6555553553403208294.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "火鼠大将应达是夜叉之一。 在魔神战争期间，她因业障而死。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "right",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/31/157749474/2b0b79e7412a1aa8d7656ed81b515250_3748238021232968632.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "每年都会庆祝海灯节以纪念守护璃月港的仙人和夜叉。节日之夜，人们将霄灯放上天空。这些灯笼的寓意是：让美德的火焰遍及世界，永不熄灭。璃月人民感谢阵亡的英雄们守护了他们的家园，点亮了霄灯，让他们漂泊的灵魂不再迷失。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "相关词条：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3797,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/21/7998136/5968bc73f375ee1e3704302541c83c7f_8796277467560472108.png",
                      "name": "璃月",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4937,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/01/10/57e3ed401d9330bedb253c03bd6ec997_1441484820862319444.png",
                      "name": "海燈節",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 46,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Zhongli_icon.png",
                      "name": "鍾離",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3487,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/22/7998136/dc0fb751f7e7704bf7a382c304817352_5244999251672933422.png",
                      "name": "歸終",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3521,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/30/7998136/61275d8b97a9c5e4055ed07a4d34c4fa_4971785901129253440.png",
                      "name": "浮舍",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 51,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xiao_icon.png",
                      "name": "魈",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3519,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/30/7998136/c11e8841d51eca4a0f5877567d0b1b28_7396795165522485074.png",
                      "name": "伐難",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3518,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/30/7998136/2a70abcd41f1c25b94da6c18901fc863_7894191907524225366.png",
                      "name": "彌怒",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2314,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/book/Yakshas: The Guardian Adepti_icon.png",
                      "name": "護法仙眾夜叉錄",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
